addr="jms-00I7">relation</fr:link> on a set <fr:tex>A</fr:tex>.</fr:p><fr:ol><fr:li>An element <fr:tex>m\in  S\subseteq  A</fr:tex> is a <fr:em><fr:strong><html:span
